description: Amex Exploration Inc., a junior mining exploration company, acquires, explores, and develops gold projects in Canada. Its flagship property is the 100% owned Perron gold project that consists of 117 mining claims covering an area of 4,836 hectares situated in Rouyn-Noranda, Quebec. It also holds interest in Lebel-Sur-Qu√©villon and Eastmain River projects located in the Abitibi region of Quebec and elsewhere in the province. The company was formerly known as Coleraine Mining Resources, Inc. Amex Exploration Inc. is based in Montreal, Canada.
